[I] An open-source implementation of the popular Go game

[T] Kigo is an open-source implementation of the popular Go game. Go is a
[T] strategic board game for two players. It is also known as igo (Japanese),
[T] weiqi or wei ch'i (Chinese) or baduk (Korean).

[U] https://apps.kde.org/kigo/

